data.description: Welcome to this beautiful brand new home! Conveniently located near Norfolk's Waterside District(downtown), Sentara Norfolk General hospital, Norfolk Naval Base and Norfolk Naval Shipyard.  Stunning features such as granite throughout (kitchen and baths), recessed lighting, waterproof laminate flooring, semi-custom cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Other features include a 3D wall, electric fireplace, custom light fixtures, primary bath w/dual vanities, and more! Beautiful newness throughout! Stop here first, this property will not disappoint! Seller to pay 3% towrds buyers closing cost!
